title: Getting Past Smoking by The Changeworks [MP3]
description:
For:
A Gentle Approach
Effective New Techniques
Cutting Down/Quitting
Enjoying Non-smoking

This CD will help whether you want to reduce your smoking habit or quit completely. The CD incorporates a variety of useful methods along with Multi-Evocation hypnosis. It will help you identify the stress triggers and psychological factors that drive the addiction and develop healthier substitutes. This approach will also help you cope with occasional urges, prevent future weight gain, and enjoy non-smoking. Use on its own or in conjunction with other stop-smoking resources.
